#

Easy Vegetable Soup

40 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasy

Description

A comforting and nutritious soup packed with fresh vegetables, perfect for a quick meal.

Ingredients

  • carrots: 2, diced
  • celery: 2 stalks, diced
  • potatoes: 2, diced
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • green beans: 1 cup, chopped
  • tomatoes: 1 can (14.5 oz), diced
  • spinach: 2 cups, fresh
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • thyme: 1 teaspoon
  • bay leaf: 1
